            <div class = 'beginner-weights'>
                <div class = 'pro-con'>
                	<h2>Pros</h2>
                    <p>Quick</p>
                    <p>Suppose to boost metabolism</p>
                    <p>Fun</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class = 'pro-con'>
                	<h2>Cons</h2>
                    <p>Fitness didnt improve much</p>
